Dear Folze,<br>
<br>
Thanks for your reply.  I appreciate what EQ has done to make this game more playerable by banning those players who duplicated items.<br>
<br>
However, I myself has never duplicated items nor possessing any such items.  And yet I was banned.  The problem comes from the fact that initially those players who duplicated items used the same credit card as I did to register. But later I used my own credit card to pay monthly payment.  In other words, the credit card I used to register is not the same as the one I used to pay monthly payments.  This means I am not the same person as those who duplicated items.  It is very unfortunate that I was banned because of their bad behaviors.<br>
<br>
I wish you can further look into this matter.  I myself has been a honest player who conforms to EQ's policy.  Hopefully I can play the game I love very much again.<br>
<br>
Your asistance will be greatly appreciated.<br>
<br>
Sincerely yours,<br>
<br>
